# Share Extension Demo iOS

![iOS](https://img.shields.io/badge/iOS-000000?style=for-the-badge&logo=ios&logoColor=white) ![Swift](https://img.shields.io/badge/swift-F54A2A?style=for-the-badge&logo=swift&logoColor=white)

Sample app to deno use of iOS Share extensions

-----------------------

## Setup

- No dependencies

## Usage

### App
- Build and run ShareDemo target in Xcode (14.2) to device or simulator

### Extension
- Build and run ShareDemoExt target in Xcode (14.2) to device or simulator

### Note
- Share extension have limited debugging only be debugged via console

